company.name: Microsoft Partner Community
company.description:
The Microsoft Partner Community is a vibrant global network of Microsoft partners driven by a shared passion for mutual assistance, knowledge sharing, collaborative projects, and continuous learning from one another.

Our Mission
Our mission is to empower the Microsoft Partner Community to be successful. We do this by providing a variety of resources, including:

A forum where partners can ask questions and get help from each other.
A blog where partners can stay up to date on the latest partner news and developments.
A library of tutorials and documentation
A calendar of events and meetups
A mentorship program that connects partners with experienced professionals
A funding program that provides financial assistance to partners who are developing innovative solutions.

How to Get Involved

There are many ways to get involved in the Microsoft Partner Community. You can:

Join our forum and ask questions or offer help to other partners.
Read our blog to stay up to date on the latest partnership news and developments.
Attend our events and meetups to meet other partners and learn from them.
Apply for our mentorship program.

We are always looking for new ways to get involved. If you have an idea for how you can help, please contact us.
